    • hitCachingCount

      private final LongAdder hitCachingCount
      The number of getBlock requests that were cache hits, but only from requests that were set to use the block cache. This is because all reads attempt to read from the block cache even if they will not put new blocks into the block cache. See HBASE-2253 for more information.
